{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016XKomhd8QHJFUWhFU5r8Ym","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `config-audit` ConfigMap is created with 11,206 bytes of findings. Here's a summary of what the audit found:\n\n---\n\n**CRITICAL (4)**\n- **C1** – `xpack.security.enabled: false` — the entire authentication/authorization subsystem is explicitly disabled. The cluster is fully open with no credentials required.\n- **C2** – TLS disabled on both HTTP (port 9200) and inter-node transport (port 9300). All traffic is plaintext. Zero TLS Secrets exist in the namespace.\n- **C3** – No `NetworkPolicy` objects exist. Any pod in the cluster can reach the ES API and transport ports unrestricted.\n- **C4** – `xpack.security.audit.enabled: false` — no forensic trail of access or configuration changes.\n\n**HIGH (3)**\n- **H1** – Pod `securityContext` is empty on all nodes; no `runAsNonRoot`, no `allowPrivilegeEscalation: false`, no seccomp profile.\n- **H2** – `audit-index` (the compliance index) has no ILM policy (`managed: false`). No retention policy governs it.\n- **H3** – `xpack.watcher.encrypt_sensitive_data: false` — Watcher action credentials stored in plaintext.\n\n**MEDIUM (4)**\n- **M1** – All nodes are `master+data+ingest` with no role separation.\n- **M2** – `updateStrategy: OnDelete` — security patches require manual pod deletion to take effect.\n- **M3** – Monitoring disabled; active CPU throttling (~44%) is invisible to operators.\n- **M4** – Version 8.11.1 from November 2023; should be evaluated against upstream CVE advisories.\n\n**Low/Info (5)**: non-default shard routing on `audit-index`, empty persistent/transient cluster settings, and confirmations of positive controls (`action.destructive_requires_name: true`, CORS disabled)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":153,"cache_read_input_tokens":48771,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":153},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4358e053-ad1e-458e-af73-bbbda8fa8007","uuid":"21861cdb-f454-4725-8328-7694ef234edb","request_id":"req_011CcLExXKxprp6arCkodtrU"}
